洋子《Go Go Cactus Man》\r\nBOLT OST《Meet Mittens》\r\nAvril《knocking on hevan's door》\r\n《Jesus bleibet miine Freud》\r\n《东方红》编钟版\r\nKILL BILL OST《Battle Without Honour》\r\n《黄河大合唱》\r\nGuns N' Roses 《don't cry》\r\nBeatles《a day in the life》\r\nBach《Prelude To Cello Suite 1 In G major》\r\n\r\n【STAFF】\r\n\r\n年轻优秀的飞行员\r\n\r\n【CAST】\r\n\r\n年轻优秀的飞行员\r\nDEERPLAY\r\n\r\n【官方网站】\r\nhttp://lixianjilixianji.blog.163.com/","date":"2009-12-05","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/3626_Tvb6r.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/3626_Tvb6r.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/3626_Tvb6r.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/3626_Tvb6r.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/0e/e8/3626_Tvb6r.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":506,"total":1943,"score":7.7,"count":{"1":9,"2":3,"3":5,"4":14,"5":41,"6":140,"7":501,"8":792,"9":324,"10":114}},"tags":[{"name":"国产","count":669},{"name":"独立动画","count":419},{"name":"短片","count":290},{"name":"李献计历险记","count":215},{"name":"2009","count":210},{"name":"差时症","count":156},{"name":"穿越","count":141},{"name":"WEB","count":101},{"name":"原创","count":92},{"name":"爱情","count":81},{"name":"国产神作","count":79}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":575,"collect":2723,"doing":17,"on_hold":44,"dropped":52}},{"id":495418,"type":2,"name":"地铁时间","name_cn":"地铁时间","summary":"北京的地铁站，陌生人们站在站台前等待地铁的到来。除了广播声音外，几乎很少有人说话，大家都沉浸在各自的世界中。少顷，列车驶入站台，人们鱼贯而入，继续刚才未完成的事。有的在悄悄聊天，有的酣然入睡，有的大嚼特嚼。而一个纤瘦的年轻人则拿出iPod，沉浸在美妙的音乐之中。突然，他看到前方一个亭亭玉立、超凡脱俗的美丽女孩。而女孩仿佛也注意到了他的存在。就在此时，车厢内的日光灯突然坏掉，接着车厢被一股强大的外力拦腰切断，一群凶残的黑色小人爬入车厢……\r\nOne Work From a student of Beijing Film Academy.\r\nYes, the student is Me.\r\nEnjoy it!!\r\n","date":"2009-12-05","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/44/bb/495418_56MM1.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/44/bb/495418_56MM1.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/44/bb/495418_56MM1.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/44/bb/495418_56MM1.jpg","common"